00Z","msg":"有人係為左環保/ 唔想再食動物而食仿真肉架嘛<br />\n佢又影響唔到你<br />\n視野唔好咁窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"睇唔出食仿肉有幾環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n少食啲牛肉可以減碳排放<br />\n<br />\n每種食物的生產多少都會耗費到水資源，但若是以一份純素餐點和一塊牛肉相比，供應肉食所耗費的水量，大約是素食的 13 倍。以生產一公斤的牛肉為例，從飼料種植、牛隻養育（包括穀類與牧草成長所需用水）、宰殺到烹調，耗費的水量就超過 3,969 加侖（15, 000 公升）的水；相當於 75 個浴缸的水量，將近是番茄的 90 倍、全麥麵包的 20 倍。<br />\n<br />\n此外，養殖場的牲畜每天所排放的污水和廢水，通常含有機質與尿液中的氨，也會間接影響環境生態的平衡，導致水污染，甚至不得不提高加氯量去消毒，而因此產生致癌物質三氯甲烷。"},{"pid":"60e36342546740ccfe18e441e36510097ccc4faa","tid":1839513,"uid":76159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"289addf7083bbb33149bdd43f5fcaa872e7905c8","tid":1839513,"uid":17799,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"cdef3aeb31305b6d796721d7c5ead0a878a6a4e3","tid":1839513,"uid":341865,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"有人係為左環保/ 唔想再食動物而食仿真肉架嘛<br />\n佢又影響唔到你<br />\n視野唔好咁窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"睇唔出食仿肉有幾環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"但啲人食仿肉唔係餐餐食<br />\n可以食咗幾日全素 先食一餐仿肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c885bbfe3f3e8151adfadd95107a767c0a6023","tid":1839513,"uid":271644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403f7e4e8c0b0c48fa4195c867d1b6fd9547dd6c","tid":1839513,"uid":76159,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5ab30f1844c520a4ee694cacff3c7da3d9305820","tid":1839513,"u