（包括穀類與牧草成長所需用水）、宰殺到烹調，耗費的水量就超過 3,969 加侖（15, 000 公升）的水；相當於 75 個浴缸的水量，將近是番茄的 90 倍、全麥麵包的 20 倍。<br />\n<br />\n此外，養殖場的牲畜每天所排放的污水和廢水，通常含有機質與尿液中的氨，也會間接影響環境生態的平衡，導致水污染，甚至不得不提高加氯量去消毒，而因此產生致癌物質三氯甲烷。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"你加工一舊植物會環保？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T01:22:24.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"5db8544c2f245e7b2ba6277b53db71c5dd7a8ccc","tid":1839513,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"死Gay婆要有一方著西裝短頭髮扮男人<br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3548b80bb2df535edce237fc5ad08d3e0bda54db","tid":1839513,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcab70d04c64810ab5fa067ebd1f623d4b12c749","tid":1839513,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"289addf7083bbb33149bdd43f5fcaa872e7905c8","tid":1839513,"uid":17799,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"cdef3aeb31305b6d796721d7c5ead0a878a6a4e3","tid":1839513,"uid":341865,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"有人係為左環保/ 唔想再食動物而食仿真肉架嘛<br />\n佢又影響唔到你<br />\n視野唔好咁窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"睇唔出食仿肉有幾環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"動物食植物<br />\n吸收率約4%<br />\n<br />\n動物食植物<br />\n吸收率20%<br />\n<br />\n即係人食動物<br />\n吸收率0.8%<br />\n<br />\n咁不如人類直接食植物<br />\n吸收率4%"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T01:49:06.000Z","msg":"人類消化唔到植物纖維"},{"pid":"19f22e72cc058e41bb2d729fc0e5ae08f30a90c7","tid":1839513,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔明"},{"pid":"5fb5aac3388b6c398c479aac1a9a3e381b96bb60","tid":1839513,"uid":683,"like":0,